  <brief_title>Anti-adhesive Effect and Safety of &quot;Thermo-sensitive Adhesion Barrier (MEDICLORE)&quot;</brief_title>
  <official_title>Anti-adhesive Effect and Safety of &quot;Thermo-sensitive Adhesion Barrier (MEDICLORE)&quot; by Using Double-blind Test in Thyroid Surgery</official_title>
